@startuml
title Hatchloom System Overview Component Diagram
top to bottom direction

actor "Student / Teacher\nParent / Admin\nEntrepreneur" as User

component "Client Application\n(Web / Mobile UI)" as Client
component "API Gateway" as Gateway

component "Auth & User Profile Service" as Auth
component "LaunchPad Service" as LaunchPad
component "ConnectHub Service" as ConnectHub

database "Persistent Data Store\n(users, sessions, profiles,\nsandboxes, sandbox_tools, side_hustles,\nbmc_sections, teams, team_members, positions,\nfeed_posts, classified_posts, messages)" as DB

interface "Position Status Interface\nGET /launchpad/positions/{id}/status" as PositionStatus

User --> Client
Client --> Gateway : HTTP requests

Gateway --> Auth : auth + profile operations
Gateway --> LaunchPad : LaunchPad APIs
Gateway --> ConnectHub : ConnectHub APIs

Auth --> DB : read/write users + sessions + profiles
LaunchPad --> DB : read/write LaunchPad tables
ConnectHub --> DB : read/write feed + classifieds + messages

LaunchPad - PositionStatus
ConnectHub --> PositionStatus : read current position state

note right of Gateway
  Routes requests, validates session,
  and enforces RBAC.
end note

note right of Auth
  Registration, login, token/session,
  and user profile management.
end note

note right of LaunchPad
  Sandbox, SideHustle, BMC,
  team, and position modules.
end note

note right of ConnectHub
  Feed, classifieds, and messaging.
end note

note right of ConnectHub
  Classifieds consult LaunchPad
  position status to determine
  OPEN/FILLED/CLOSED behavior.
end note

@enduml